rows.label: qev085701_MSG0001
rows.name:
Yo, Elma, good timing.
I just got a juicy tip—care to get in on it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0003
rows.name:
Wha— Seriously?!
Don't you even want to hear what it is first?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0004
rows.name:
Something tells me if it was that "juicy,"
you wouldn't be approaching me about it like this...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0005
rows.name: Oh c'mon, you make me sound like a con man.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0006
rows.name:
You could at least FEIGN interest, you know.
Common courtesy and all that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0007
rows.name: Ah, common courtesy... You mean back on Earth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0008
rows.name: Yeah I know we're on Mira now and all but still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0009
rows.name: All right, Doug, all right. Let's hear it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085701_MSG0010
rows.name:
That's more like it. Meet me in back of the diner in the
industrial district, okay? Fewer ears there, you know?[ST:wait ]
